    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span><strong> boiled water</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and <strong>chopped tomatoes</strong> to the softened onion with your <strong>Henderson's Relish</strong> and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>",
