    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-low and cook for 10-15 min or until it thickens to resemble a pasta sauce-like consistency</p><p>While the sauce thickens, drain and rinse your <strong>cannellini beans</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>cannellini beans</strong> to the sauce, reduce the heat to low and warm through until you're ready to serve – these are your <strong>Indian-style beans</strong></p>",
